heading: Twisted Hollow Dungeon Guide
content: Twisted Hollow is a short dungeon with the . The Animus Carriers make for extra elites for extra loot, and the boss is fast and easy to kill. If there's a Nightmare Dungeon here, you may want to consider completing the Sigil! While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! This dungeon is not accessible until you cleanse out the evil in . This unlocks the Dungeon. This can be done solo, but goes by quicker with a group of friends. Reviewed by
